pgcl-testscripts — licensing
============================

Copyright (c) 2026 Nadia Yvette Chambers <nadia.yvette.chambers@ik.me>
and contributors.

This project (test scripts, QEMU/boot harnesses, reproducers, the rmap
debug toolkit, nolibc bring-up inits, and supporting C/asm/Python/shell)
is the original work of the copyright holder, assembled to develop and
validate the Linux page-clustering (PGCL / "larpage") forward-port.

